Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.65,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\frz6.582\pos(290,480)}申请者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.65,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.44\pos(410,464)}纠缠闪电 所属/哈美伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.65,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.813\pos(284,600)}进入
